43
00:03:11,703 --> 00:03:12,726
And where might

44
00:03:12,742 --> 00:03:14,109
the bride's relatives be found?

45
00:03:14,234 --> 00:03:16,108
I had hoped to make their acquaintance,

46
00:03:16,133 --> 00:03:18,155
as you and the lady are soon to be wed.

47
00:03:19,992 --> 00:03:22,326
