51
00:03:32,108 --> 00:03:33,841
My coming alone suffices.

52
00:03:34,701 --> 00:03:36,240
Regardless, I remain grateful

53
00:03:36,265 --> 00:03:37,677
for your compassion.

54
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:39,490
