left little wealth.

72
00:04:13,068 --> 00:04:14,365
But when Malai assumes

73
00:04:14,390 --> 00:04:15,795
the role of my daughter-in-law,

74
00:04:15,818 --> 00:04:16,841
she shall no longer

75
00:04:16,850 --> 00:04:17,935
be reliant on others.

76
00:04:18,131 --> 00:04:19,240
And I hope none

77
00:04:20,326 --> 00:04:22,326
would trouble my daughter-in-law.

78
00:04:25,639 --> 00:04:26,639
Umm... And,

79
00:04:28,287 --> 00:04:30,763
Where might Miss Malai be found?

80
00:04:31,272 --> 00:04:33,162
I wish to see if she is truly as comely

81
00:04:33,178 --> 00:04:35,224
as Fueang has praised her to be.

82
00:05:45,851 --> 00:05:46,851
Thank you.

83
00:05:57,932 --> 00:05:58,932
Thank you.

84
00:06:50,973 --> 00:06:52,535
May you both be blessed

85
00:06:52,551 --> 00:06:54,254
with offspring aplenty

86
00:07:00,128 --> 00:07:02,205
and revel in each other's company

87
00:07:02,213 --> 00:07:04,480
