88
00:07:05,885 --> 00:07:07,085
Thank you, sir.

89
00:07:25,229 --> 00:07:26,229
Malai!

90
00:07:28,354 --> 00:07:29,474
Ms. Bu-nga!

91
00:07:47,167 --> 00:07:48,287
