93
00:07:54,901 --> 00:07:55,901
My name is Bu-nga,

94
00:07:56,268 --> 00:07:57,346
the daughter of

95
00:07:57,362 --> 00:07:58,854
the Eastern Trade Minister.

96
00:07:59,401 --> 00:08:00,822
