97
00:08:03,479 --> 00:08:05,549
Pleasure to make your acquaintance, all.

98
00:08:12,151 --> 00:08:13,971
Nice to meet you, Ms. Bu-nga.

99
00:08:15,698 --> 00:08:17,088
