The red cotton flower tea has run out.

126
00:09:16,229 --> 00:09:17,494
Fear not, my lord.

127
00:09:17,511 --> 00:09:19,189
We can gather the red cotton flowers

128
00:09:19,214 --> 00:09:20,681
