Today is sunny,

192
00:17:00,470 --> 00:17:02,196
we can gather the red cotton flowers

193
00:17:02,205 --> 00:17:03,696
to dry and make tea in time.

194
00:17:05,970 --> 00:17:07,532
I shall assist Uan.

195
00:17:11,752 --> 00:17:13,244
Thank you, Ms. Malai,

196
00:17:13,269 --> 00:17:14,867
for protecting me.

197
00:17:14,892 --> 00:17:16,369
Otherwise, the lord would have

198
00:17:16,392 --> 00:17:17,986
given me a hard time.

199
00:17:18,017 --> 00:17:19,165
It is nothing.

200
00:17:19,182 --> 00:17:20,423
This is a trifling matter.

201
00:17:21,033 --> 00:17:23,306
