204
00:17:28,213 --> 00:17:29,369
Why did you not pick

205
00:17:29,394 --> 00:17:31,353
the red cotton flowers and dry them?

206
00:17:31,369 --> 00:17:32,619
There was a heavy downpour

207
00:17:32,643 --> 00:17:33,843
the other day,

208
00:17:34,205 --> 00:17:35,376
