210
00:17:36,518 --> 00:17:38,025
it didn't fall down, ma'am.

211
00:17:38,549 --> 00:17:39,681
The male servants

212
00:17:40,314 --> 00:17:41,626
were dispatched to work

213
00:17:41,651 --> 00:17:43,142
at Sanam Chan Palace for the lord,

214
00:17:43,167 --> 00:17:44,587
