215
00:17:44,603 --> 00:17:46,736
didn't dare climb and pluck the flowers.

216
00:17:46,752 --> 00:17:48,572
They're afraid it might fall on them.

217
00:17:50,080 --> 00:17:51,220
I see.

218
00:17:52,549 --> 00:17:53,720
Next time,

219
00:17:53,745 --> 00:17:55,736
if you notice anything in short supply,

220
00:17:55,761 --> 00:17:56,939
please store it

221
00:17:57,502 --> 00:17:59,369
so you won't incur his wrath again.

222
00:17:59,736 --> 00:18:01,361
